result.title: ADA 30: 30 Tips for 30 Years // Tips 21-30 - Effective Communication
result.description:
July 26, 2020 is the 30th Anniversary of the Americans with Disabilities Act.  This landmark law changed the lives of millions of individuals with disabilities, and its application continues to increase access and opportunity for individuals across the United States.  In conjunction with this monumentous occasion, Seyfarth Shaw's ADA Title III Team put together a video series with 30 practical tips for businesses to better serve people with disabilities, and comply with the law.  We think you'll find that these tips are practical, and not all that hard to follow.  We hope you will share these tips within your business.

To learn more about the ADA and the Title III Team, please visit: https://www.adatitleiii.com/

Check out Parts 1 & 2 here:
https://youtu.be/RhpweF-K7Fc
